Source: qt-components
Section: libs 
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Antonio Aloisio <antonio.aloisio@nokia.com>
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5), quilt, libqt4-dev(>= 4.7.0~), libqt4-declarative, libmeegotouch-dev
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: qt-components
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Qt Quick components runtime libraries
 The qt-components project aims to deliver a set of reusable components for Qt Quick.
 Qt Quick provides simple QML Elements that allow you to create fluid uis from scratch without restricting 
 the designers creativity.
 .
 Homepage: http://labs.qt.nokia.com/2010/09/10/building-the-future-reintroducing-the-qt-quick-components/
 Bugs: http://bugreports.qt.nokia.com/browse/QTCOMPONENTS 
 Code: http://qt.gitorious.org/qt-components

